Somewhat funny, typical ending, disappointed because I thought it was another movie I briefly saw years ago, it starred Lisa Nicole Carson, a actor named Khail,and Nicole Parker among others, it was about a urban singing girl group, great acting and musical numbers, but it seemed to disappeared,haven't seen it on tv and haven't seen it available as a DVD, kinda of a shame,it's a early reminder of many of the prominent blacks actors of today that I see guest starring on many tv shows. Hopefully it will be reissued.
